 Write, open paren, 1, buff, n, close paren, semicolon, close curly brace.

46
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:19,000
 If the file size is not an exact multiple of buff size, some read will return a smaller number of bytes to be written by write.

47
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:23,000
 The next call after that read will return 0.

48
